GD Practice:

Topic:
👉 “Is social media good or bad for youth?”

GPE Practice:

👉 Situation:
You see:

Accident victim
Train to catch in 30 min

👉 What will you do?

🧠 SECRET TIP

👉 GTO observes:

How you speak
How you behave
How you help group

👉 Not just WHAT you say

